{"tid":872122,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有巴絲去過岡山奥津溪嗎？","createTime":"2018-10-22T12:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T01:45:38.000Z","uid":185110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbba745e9197e6983cded8fe6e877bb99917168","tid":872122,"uid":185110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"想去睇紅葉，但我無訂奥津溫泉，會即日來回大阪。<br />\n<br />\n我宜家有兩個plan，一係1230入到去，然後搭1430車出番津山；一係1320入到去，但要1720先有得走。<br />\n<br />\n想問個度係咪得紅葉景區，預1.5小時夠嗎？<br />\n如果1.5小時唔夠睇，想問個頭有無食肆或便利店？<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴絲！"},{"pid":"cd1df26412c3066ce41b5b230049e1e8d5f60560","tid":872122,"uid":185110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48d64abb83b05d1f2d8a6bb27698671539ab84d2","tid":872122,"uid":185110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"求解答"}]}